Test harness for the RESULTS report. QUERY votes WHERE poll_id EQ PARAM.poll_id INTO poll_votes, TABULATE COUNT FOR option VS voter_tag INTO matrix, then PRINT MATCHED:N, TAB_ROWS:N, and the JSON matrix via PRINT TABULATE AS JSON. Lets developers verify that filtering and tabulation sizes look right end-to-end before relying on the RESULTS output. Accepts PARAM.poll_id. Used for debugging RESULTS regressions; not called from the frontend.
